<pb n="0030c" id="T19.0924C.0030c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0030c02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 924C</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0030c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0030031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】大日本續藏經</note>藥師儀軌一具</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0030c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c0501">若欲入向道場者。先澡浴清淨。以真言手印。
<lb n="0030c06" ed="T"/>灑淨所換之衣。次以真言加持其衣而著。真
<lb n="0030c07" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c0801" type="dharani">唵微&CB00757;羅莎縛賀</p>
<lb n="0030c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c0901">次即衣著。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c1001" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;哩&CB00085;羅多&CB00085;曰里尼吽</p>
<lb n="0030c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c1101">次飲水灑淨。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c1201" type="dharani">唵摩訶入&CB00085;羅吽</p>
<lb n="0030c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c1301">次入向道場時。不起貪欲瞋恚等。專念本尊
<lb n="0030c14" ed="T"/>而住<note place="inline">住自他本清淨。步步想踐連華&CB01191;</note>次至道場門外灑淨<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0030c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c1501">次香水灑身。以後稱吽字三聲。然後道場并
<lb n="0030c16" ed="T"/>觀想聖眾。遍滿道場。如影重之。不相妨礙。次
<lb n="0030c17" ed="T"/>入道場已。面向於本尊。合掌作禮。禮三部尊。
<lb n="0030c18" ed="T"/>及本尊已。舉頭諦觀佛菩薩金剛像也。向佛
<lb n="0030c19" ed="T"/>陳說三世宿愆惡障。重懺本尊所。亦如是懺
<lb n="0030c20" ed="T"/>禮。偈曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT19p0030c2101"><l>我從過去世</l><l>流轉於生死</l>
<lb n="0030c22" ed="T"/><l>今對大聖尊</l><l>盡心而懺悔</l>
<lb n="0030c23" ed="T"/><l>如先佛所懺</l><l>我今亦如是</l>
<lb n="0030c24" ed="T"/><l>願承加持力</l><l>眾生悉清淨</l>
<lb n="0030c25" ed="T"/><l>以此大願故</l><l>自他獲無垢</l></lg>
<lb n="0030c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c2601">次香水淨三業。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c2701" type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;輸馱薩&CB00085;達麼薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;</p>
<lb n="0030c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c2801">輸度啥次定心已。作三部三昧耶。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0030c2901" type="dharani">唵怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;&CB00418;納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛<note place="inline">引</note>也娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">佛</note></p>
<pb n="0031a" id="T19.0924C.0031a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0101" type="dharani">唵跛娜謨<note place="inline">二合</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛<note place="inline">引</note>也娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">蓮</note></p>
<lb n="0031a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0201" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰盧<note place="inline">二合</note>納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>縛也婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0031a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0301" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">已上三部三昧耶</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0401">次遣除身中毘那夜迦。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0501" type="dharani">唵闍波沒&CB00069;帝賀囊迦囊吽泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0601">次辟除諸障。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0701" type="dharani">曩謨&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅也吽賀囊&CB00757;他尾特夢婆輸&CB03586;羅
<lb n="0031a08" ed="T"/>也泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a0901">次辟除諸物所有諸難<note place="inline">在多意云云</note>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1001" type="dharani">唵枳哩枳哩羅&CB00085;嗟捺羅&CB00292;泮吒<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1101">次去垢真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1201" type="dharani">唵枳哩枳哩&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅&CB00292;泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1301">次清淨。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1401" type="dharani">唵爾囊爾迦</p>
<lb n="0031a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1501">次光澤。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1601" type="dharani">唵帝誓帝惹徒尾寧徒提沙馱吽泮吒<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a1701">次神分。次唱禮。一切恭敬。次供文。次四方四
<lb n="0031a18" ed="T"/>佛四菩薩。次本尊稱名三遍。次三部界會一
<lb n="0031a19" ed="T"/>切佛菩薩等。次驚覺。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2001" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;曰魯<note place="inline">二合用</note>底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0031a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2101"><note place="inline">印者。二手各金剛拳。舒頭指。各頭側相柱二小指相交。每誦一遍。作印拳動</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2201">次九方便　至心歸命。</p>
<lb n="0031a23" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT19p0031a2301"><l>歸命十方正等覺</l><l>三世一切具三身</l>
<lb n="0031a24" ed="T"/><l>歸命一切大乘法</l><l>歸命不退菩提眾</l>
<lb n="0031a25" ed="T"/><l>歸命諸明真實言</l><l>歸命一切諸密印</l>
<lb n="0031a26" ed="T"/><l>以身口意清淨業</l><l>慇懃無量恭敬禮</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2701">歸命頂禮藥師&CB00222;璃光佛。</p>
<lb n="0031a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2801">次禮方便。真言曰<note place="inline">印者。以金剛部印。當額誦&CB00057;禮拜</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031a2901" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>曩莫薩縛怛他<note place="inline">引</note>蘗多<note place="inline">二</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>野弭縛<note place="inline">引</note>
<pb n="0031b" id="T19.0924C.0031b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031b01" ed="T"/>吃質<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">三</note>縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>滿娜南迦嚕弭</p>
<lb n="0031b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b0201">次至心歸依。次真言<note place="inline">印者金剛合掌</note>次施身方便了。
<lb n="0031b03" ed="T"/>歸命頂禮。施身方便。真言如例。印者。金剛
<lb n="0031b04" ed="T"/>合掌。投身舒耳。若莊校投者。運心耳。次至心
<lb n="0031b05" ed="T"/>發願了。歸命頂禮。發菩提心方便真言。次至
<lb n="0031b06" ed="T"/>心懺悔了。歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。先金剛合掌。大指頭指舒著</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b0701">次至心隨喜了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。金剛合掌</note>次
<lb n="0031b08" ed="T"/>至心勸請了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">印者。金剛合掌</note>次
<lb n="0031b09" ed="T"/>至心奉請誦了。次歸命頂禮。次真言<note place="inline">先作向清印。入內
<lb n="0031b10" ed="T"/>大指更出舌。頭指鉤召</note>次至心迴向誦了。次歸命頂禮。次
<lb n="0031b11" ed="T"/>真言如例<note place="inline">印金剛合掌云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1201">次護身。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1301" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB02915;&CB00135;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;羅捻跛跢<note place="inline">二合引</note>也娑
<lb n="0031b14" ed="T"/>縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0031b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1501">次大護身真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1601" type="dharani">唵入&CB00085;羅囊也&CB00292;泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1701">次被甲真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1801" type="dharani">唵度比度比迦也度比&CB00425;羅入&CB00085;里寧娑婆賀</p>
<lb n="0031b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b1901">次結髮。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2001" type="dharani">唵蘇悉地羯哩莎&CB00085;賀</p>
<lb n="0031b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2101">次結地界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2201" type="dharani">唵枳里枳里&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>縛曰里<note place="inline">二合</note>部律<note place="inline">二合半音</note>
<lb n="0031b23" ed="T"/>滿馱滿馱吽發吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0031b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2401">次結方隅金剛<note n="0031001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">幡＝&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0031001" resp="【原】" corr="">幡</sic>。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2501" type="dharani">唵薩羅薩羅縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0031002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（&CB00425;羅）&M062485;＋伽【原】</note><sic n="0031002" resp="【原】" corr="＆CB00425；羅伽">伽</sic>羅吽泮吒<note place="inline">半音</note></p>
<lb n="0031b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2601">次置寶座等。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2701" type="dharani">唵毘&CB00757;嚕挪地&CB00292;<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2801">次阿者羅吽<note place="inline">三遍</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031b2901" type="dharani">唵阿者羅微&CB03272;娑婆賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<pb n="0031c" id="T19.0924C.0031c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0101" type="dharani">唵迦&CB00757;羅娑婆賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0201" type="dharani">唵囊&CB00757;薩&CB00085;怛他&CB00617;哆南薩羅&CB00085;他欠烏跢&CB00617;
<lb n="0031c03" ed="T"/>帝娑破羅呬&CB00757;<note n="0031003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔闍〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0031003" resp="【原】" corr="＆lac；">闍</sic>伽伽囊&CB01894;娑&CB00085;賀<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0031c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0401">次以我功德力。如來加持力。及以法界力。普
<lb n="0031c05" ed="T"/>供養而住。</p>
<lb n="0031c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0601">次大虛空藏普通供養真言并印。</p>
<lb n="0031c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0701" type="dharani">唵&CB00344;&CB00344;曩三<note place="inline">去</note>婆&CB00085;&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0031c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c0801">次遏伽以辨事真言持誦。後以部母&CB00057;&CB00057;之。
<lb n="0031c09" ed="T"/>置於左邊。</p>
<lb n="0031c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1001">次部母。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1101" type="dharani">娜牟婆伽婆都烏瑟尼沙耶唵盧盧娑普嚧若
<lb n="0031c12" ed="T"/>&CB00085;羅帝瑟佗悉陀嚕者&CB00135;薩&CB00085;羅他娑但&CB00135;莎
<lb n="0031c13" ed="T"/>訶</p>
<lb n="0031c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1401">次於寶座上。觀本尊種子字。并結根本印<note place="inline">云
<lb n="0031c15" ed="T"/>云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1601">次轉字成本尊。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1701" type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南</p>
<lb n="0031c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c1801">次欲請本尊。先執香爐。誦真言。淨治空中道
<lb n="0031c19" ed="T"/>路。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2001" type="dharani">唵蘇悉地迦里入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>里多南多暮羅<note place="inline">二<app><lem wit="【CBETA】">合</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note>曳
<lb n="0031c21" ed="T"/>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅滿馱滿馱賀囊賀囊&CB00292;泮吒</p>
<lb n="0031c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2201">次發願啟白眾。</p>
<lb n="0031c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2301">次奉請本尊。更先想座已也。成就車輅。送本
<lb n="0031c24" ed="T"/>尊所<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p>
<lb n="0031c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2501">寶車輅。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2601" type="dharani">唵都嚕都嚕吽</p>
<lb n="0031c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2701">次請車輅。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0031c2801" type="dharani">娜麼悉底哩野<note place="inline">二合</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>南怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;
<lb n="0031c29" ed="T"/>多<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">引一</note>唵&CB00085;曰郎<note place="inline">二合</note>銀&CB00135;野<note place="inline">三合引</note>羯唎沙
<pb n="0032a" id="T19.0924C.0032a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032a01" ed="T"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0201">次召請奉本尊。真真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0301" type="dharani">唵枳里枳里&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅吽泮吒<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0401">次<note n="0032001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原本冠註曰視字更勘</note>視三昧耶。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0501" type="dharani">唵昇羯&CB03740;三&CB00757;&CB00195;莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0601">次奉閼伽。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0701" type="dharani">唵藥乞私囊那也見捺羅達弩&CB00425;捨莎訶<note place="inline">三遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0801">次奉蓮華座<note place="inline">誦三部真言。獻成用道用</note>。</p>
<lb n="0032a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a0901" type="dharani">唵味羅味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1001" type="dharani">唵&CB00425;那&CB00757;味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1101" type="dharani">唵縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅味羅也莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1201">次陳善來世尊真言。持誦奉獻。</p>
<lb n="0032a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1301">次結上方金剛網。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1401" type="dharani">唵尾娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>羅捺落<note place="inline">二合</note>乞刃<note place="inline">二合</note>縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0032a15" ed="T"/>半惹羅吽泮吒</p><p id="pT19p0032a1507" place="inline">次上下方。</p>
<lb n="0032a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1601">次火院真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1701" type="dharani">唵阿三&CB00757;擬&CB00135;吽泮吒</p>
<lb n="0032a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1801">次重結大界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a1901" type="dharani">唵昇羯&CB03740;&CB00757;訶三摩焰莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a2001">次奉塗香。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a2101" type="dharani">伊&CB01215;言馱輸婆&CB00135;微夜<note place="inline">二合</note>輸者也輸者輸者
<lb n="0032a22" ed="T"/>輸者也&CB00757;夜&CB00135;吠&CB00135;始薄訖底也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0032a23" ed="T"/>底仡&CB00069;呬也&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>四椰&CB01215;唵阿賀羅阿賀
<lb n="0032a24" ed="T"/>羅薩羅縛尾&CB00135;夜達羅布爾帝莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a2501">奉華真言</p>
<lb n="0032a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032a2601" type="dharani">伊&CB01215;蘇&CB00757;囊素&CB00135;尾夜輪者輸輸者輸囊也莽
<lb n="0032a27" ed="T"/>夜寧唵伏&CB00135;多薄訖底<note place="inline">二合</note>夜&CB00425;羅底仡&CB00069;呬
<lb n="0032a28" ed="T"/>也&CB00425;羅四挪&CB01215;唵阿賀羅阿賀羅薩羅縛尾&CB00135;
<lb n="0032a29" ed="T"/>夜達羅布爾帝莎訶</p>
<pb n="0032b" id="T19.0924C.0032b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b0101">奉燒香。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b0201" type="dharani">阿閻縛囊沙&CB00425;底羅素賀&CB00069;&CB00135;也健陀值也蘇
<lb n="0032b03" ed="T"/>羅部若曩莽夜寧吠&CB00135;始薄訖底夜度報閻&CB00425;
<lb n="0032b04" ed="T"/>羅底仡&CB00069;呬也難唵阿<note place="inline">去</note>賀羅阿賀羅薩羅縛
<lb n="0032b05" ed="T"/>尾&CB00135;夜達羅布爾莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b0601">奉食。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b0701" type="dharani">奧灑涕難羅素賀&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>他也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00799;灑涌多羅
<lb n="0032b08" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>設怒麼里莽也寧唵吠&CB00135;始薄訖底夜<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0032b09" ed="T"/>&CB00425;羅底仡呬也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;羅四椰吽唵阿<note place="inline">去</note>羅賀
<lb n="0032b10" ed="T"/>阿羅賀薩羅縛尾&CB00135;夜<note place="inline">二合</note>達羅布爾帝莎訶</p>
<lb n="0032b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b1101">奉燈。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b1201" type="dharani">羅訖&CB00034;<note place="inline">二合</note>近曩<note place="inline">二合</note>灑者<note place="inline">二合</note>跛尾怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>室
<lb n="0032b13" ed="T"/>者<note place="inline">二合</note>瞻謨尾曇莽曩<note place="inline">短名</note>輸婆莽夜寧吠&CB00135;始
<lb n="0032b14" ed="T"/>薄訖底夜<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;報閻&CB00425;羅底訖&CB00069;<note place="inline">二合</note>呬也難
<lb n="0032b15" ed="T"/>唵阿路迦也薩羅尾&CB00135;夜<note place="inline">二合</note>達羅布爾帝莎
<lb n="0032b16" ed="T"/>婆賀</p>
<lb n="0032b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b1701">次運心供養。以心運想。水陸諸華。無<note n="0032002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曰字更勘</note>曰主
<lb n="0032b18" ed="T"/>所。遍滿虛空。盡十方界。及以人天。妙塗香
<lb n="0032b19" ed="T"/>雲。燒香燈明。幢幡寶蓋。種種鼓樂。歌舞妓
<lb n="0032b20" ed="T"/>唱。真珠羅網。懸諸寶領。<note n="0032003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">髣白…網（十一字）更勘</note>髣白拂微妙聲。鋒
<lb n="0032b21" ed="T"/>矜羯尼網。如意寶樹。衣服之雲天。諸廚膳上。
<lb n="0032b22" ed="T"/>妙香美味。宮殿樓閣寶柱。莊嚴身。頭冠瓔珞。
<lb n="0032b23" ed="T"/>如是等雲。行者運心。遍滿虛空。以至誠心。如
<lb n="0032b24" ed="T"/>是供養。最為勝上。是故行者以決定心。而行
<lb n="0032b25" ed="T"/>此法。運心供養。誦持真言。及作手印。如上
<lb n="0032b26" ed="T"/>所想。皆悉成就。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b2701" type="dharani">唵薩羅&CB00085;他龕搵娜&CB03442;帝娑頗羅呬門伽伽曩
<lb n="0032b28" ed="T"/>&CB01894;莎訶<note place="inline">七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0032b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0032b2901">次讚歎佛曰。</p>
